divs: Sighting Detailsi though it was a star in the sunrise, but it was bright and below the cloud bank at one point. i took a camera out because it was bright but it disappeared as soon as i looked into the viewfinder. I see stars alot because of clear skies here, so i know what a start could look while the sun is coming up. and i was on the beach next to america's PMRF missle range, where there has been experimental testing the past few months
